# Shared CH5 packages (@ch5me/ch5-ui-web, ch5-design-web, firefly-design, ...)
# are published to GitHub Packages. Auth (NODE_AUTH_TOKEN) comes from the user's
# ~/.npmrc locally or from CI secrets — intentionally NOT set here so this file
# carries no token. Our own @ch5me/storygen-* packages resolve from the
# workspace and never hit this registry.
@ch5me:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com/
